<div class='flex flex-col space-y-16'>
  <section class='space-y-16 text-center'>
    <h1 class="font-semibold text-4xl">🪄 One click blog from your Instagram.</h1>

    <div>
      <% if current_user %>
        <%= link_to 'Open app', user_path, class: 'bg-violet-700 hover:bg-violet-900 text-fuchsia-50 p-4 rounded-md font-bold' %>
      <% else %>
        <%= link_to '🎯 Connect your Instagram', users_sign_in_path, class: 'bg-violet-700 hover:bg-violet-900 text-fuchsia-50 p-4 rounded-md font-bold' %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class='space-y-8'>
    <h2 class='font-semibold text-3xl text-center'>🧐 How it works</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-center">
      <div class='bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-500 via-purple-500 to-pink-500 rounded-lg p-4 text-white'>
        <div class='text-4xl'>1. 🔑</div>
        <div>Connect your Instagram account to Insta2Blog</div>
      </div>
      <div class='bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-500 via-purple-500 to-pink-500 rounded-lg p-4 text-white'>
        <div class='text-4xl'>2. ✍️</div>
        <div>Post on Instagram, as usual</div>
      </div>
      <div class='bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-500 via-purple-500 to-pink-500 rounded-lg p-4 text-white'>
        <div class='text-4xl'>3. 🧘‍♀️</div>
        <div>Relax</div>
      </div>
    </div> 

    <div class='text-gray-700 text-xl'>
      Every time you post on Instagram, we will 🪄🦄 automagically create a SEO-perfect blog post on your insta2blog website.
    </div>

    <% if @random_user.present? %>
      <div class='text-gray-700 text-xl'>
        For example, if your account on instagram is <b><%= @random_user.username %></b>, your blog posts will be at <b><%= link_to insta_user_posts_url(@random_user), insta_user_posts_url(@random_user) %></b>.
      </div>
    <% end %>

    <div class='text-center'>
      <%= link_to '👀 See examples', insta_users_path, class: 'bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-800 text-fuchsia-50 p-4 rounded-md font-bold' %>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class='space-y-4'>
    <h2 class='font-semibold text-3xl text-center'>⁉️ What for?</h2>
    <div class='space-y-4 text-lg'>
      <div>
        🧘‍♀️ Run a blog without the tension of maintaining a blog.
      </div>

      <div>
        🥇 Boost your SEO ranking. Instagram posts do not rank in Google. Yours will.
      </div>

      <div>
        🔗 Anybody can link to your content. Avoid the instagram "registration wall".
      </div>

      <div>
        🧐 Own the experience on your blog. Don't compete for attention with other creators on Instagram.
      </div>

      <div>
        ♻️ Make your content "evergreen". Give a second life to old posts by making them more accessible. 
      </div>

      <div>
        🔍 Quick search for posts on your profile.
      </div>

      <div>
        #️⃣ #hashtag & @mention search only inside YOUR content. Don't redirect traffic out of your blog!
      </div>

      <div>
        💾 Backup your Instagram profile. Don't lose your stuff if you get banned by any chance.
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <%# <h2 class='font-bold text-3xl text-center'>📧 Get notified about the launch 🚀</h2> %>
</div>
